#                                                                             #
# Description:                                                                #
#    Test Cases of Dynamic System Variable log that checks the behavior of    #
#    this variable in the following ways                                      #
#              * Default Value                                                #
#              * Valid & Invalid values                                       #
#              * Scope & Access method                                        #
#              * Data Integrity                                               #
